    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable transportation option for someone on a budget. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car has high mileage and will require some mechanical attention soon, such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some early signs of surface rust on the rear wheel wells. The interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get cold, but overall, it remains a solid, drivable car for its age.",
