    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You are going to absolutely love this ride. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, so there isn't a speck of dust or a scratch to be found. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
